stimulus: Welcome to the experiment. Press any key to get started.

You will see a set of 10 symbols arranged in a circle.

Sometimes all of the symbols will match. Other times one of the symbols will be different than the others.

Press the A key when one symbol is different. Press the L key when all symbols are the same.

Press any key to continue.

In this set of trials, a fixation cross will be presented to you in the center of the screen.

Please focus your gaze on the fixation cross in the center until the symbol set is presented.

Press any key to continue.

Now you will complete three trials for practice.

Press the A key if one of the symbols does not match and the L key if they all match.

Press any key when you are ready to begin.

Now you will proceed to the test trials.

Press the A key if one of the symbols does not match and the L key if they all match.

Press any key when you are ready to begin.

Now the symbols will switch, where the target symbol will now be the nontarget and vice versa.

The rest of the procedure will remain the same for the next chunk of trials, so please continue to press the A key if one of the symbols does not match and the L key if they are all the same.

Press any key when you are ready to continue.

In this set of trials, the mismatching symbol will be presented to you in the center of the screen. You can use it as a reference to find the target.

Please focus your gaze on the symbol in the center until the symbol set is presented.

Press any key to continue.

Now you will complete three trials for practice.

Press the A key if one of the symbols does not match and the L key if they all match.

Press any key when you are ready to begin.

Now you will proceed to the test trials.

Press the A key if one of the symbols does not match and the L key if they all match.

Press any key when you are ready to begin.

Now the symbols will switch, where the target symbol will now be the nontarget and vice versa.

The rest of the procedure will remain the same for the next chunk of trials, so please continue to press the A key if one of the symbols does not match and the L key if they are all the same.

Press any key when you are ready to continue.

The stimuli used in this experiment could have been conceptualized as alpha-numeric symbols such as rotated 2s and 5s or Us and Ns. In your trials, did you use any alpha-numeric symbols such as these to help you identify the symbols?

Press the key A for Yes. Press the key L for No.
